              <br>2- the video that you submit will be <strong>private</strong> and only you can see the page.\n                                <br>3- <strong>be very clear about what you want to trade!</strong>\n                                <br>4- <strong>please do not upload any videos yet and please do not send us any links in this request!</strong>\n                                <br>5- state the information of your video(s)(name, genre, link to original source if possible).\n                                <br>6- state the information of the video(s) that you want from us('+gardenArray[1].appFullName+').\n\n                                <br>7- lets keep the trade <strong>fair</strong>, so:\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7a- in case of videos, we will only trade 1 video VS 1 video.</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7b- in case of VIP or PREMIUM, we will only trade 1 website credentials(membership) VS 1 VIP or 1 PREMIUM code.</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7c- we will not trade our 4K and HD videos against low resolution videos.</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7d- we will not trade our full movies against 3 minute clips.</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7e- we will cancel the trade if your video is not original(for example: if you downloaded it from a streaming site).</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7f- <strong>(only applies to credential trade)</strong>we will only trade an *upgrade against credentials that are valid for at least 7 full days.</span>\n                                <br><span class="color-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp;7g- <strong>(only applies to download site credential trade)</strong>we will only trade an *upgrade against credentials that are valid for at least 14 full days.</span>\n<br>8- you can (for obvious reasons) only request videos posted on '+gardenArray[1].appFullName+'.<br>9- we can (for obvious reasons) only accept videos that represent the already displayed fetishes within this platform.<br>\n10- we do not accept videos coming from the following sites/stores:<br>\n<span class="color-danger">newmfx.com</span>, <span class="color-danger">mfvideofetish.com</span>, <span class="color-danger">thenewgirlspooping.com</span>, <span class="color-danger">fartfantasy.com</span>, <span class="color-danger">lesbianassworship.net</span>                             <br><br><small>*a PREMIUM or VIP upgrade</small>\n                            </p></div><div class="margin-top-0 callout-elem callout-elem-danger">\n                            <h4>DONTS</h4>\n<p><i class="color-warning fa fa-warning"></i> 10a- DO NOT TRY TO TRADE VIDEOS THAT ARE NOT RARE!<br><i class="color-warning fa fa-warning"></i> 10b- DO NOT TRY TO TRADE VIDEOS THAT ARE NOT FROM THE ORIGINAL SOURCE!<br><i class="color-warning fa fa-warning"></i> 10c- DO NOT TRY TO TRADE VIDEOS THAT ARE NOT PURCHASED BY YOURSELF!<br> <i class="color-warning fa fa-warning"></i> 10d- DO NOT TRY TO TRADE VIDEOS THAT ARE DOWNLOADED FROM A STREAMING SITE, A POPULAR BLOG OR A POPULAR DOWNLOAD SITE!</p></div>'),"dmca"==$scope.page&&(FilthyMdl.pageTitle("DMCA"),$scope.subject="Copyright Issues",$scope.description=""),$scope.subject||$scope.goTo("/"),setTimeout(function(){$("#descriptionHtml").html($.parseHTML($scope.description))},50);var original;$scope.form={message:""},$scope.canSubmit=function(){return $scope.form_message.$valid&&!angular.equals($scope.form,original)},$scope.submitSendContactForm=function(){ContactSrv.sendMessage({form:$scope.form,subject:$rootScope.pageTitle},userInfo,function(response){loggit.logSuccess("Thank you for contacting us. Your message has been sent. We will contact you within 24 hours if necessary."),$location.url("/dashboard/")})}}}]).controlle